      <p>Every new user earns a 1000 XEM joining bonus across 4 milestones: Signup (100), Profile complete (100), KYC approved (300), First payment received (500).</p>
      <h3>Earned vs Bonus XEM</h3>
      <p><strong>Earned XEM</strong> — from invoice payments (1 XEM per $1 NET received). Always redeemable once you are KYC-verified, no extra gate.</p>
